Label: Manufacturer
Description: A manufacturing organization (from IOF Core Ontology)

Label: GeospatialSite
Description: A physical location with geographic coordinates

Label: Capability
Description: A capability that an organization possesses (from IOF Core)

Label: ProductionCapability
Description: Production or manufacturing capability (from IOF Supply Chain)

Label: ManufacturingProcessCapability
Description: A specific manufacturing process capability (parent class for ~400 process types)

Label: MaterialProcessingCapability
Description: A material processing capability (parent class for ~300 material types)

Label: Certificate
Description: Quality or professional certification (parent class for ~50 certificate types)

Label: Industry
Description: An industry sector or classification (parent class)

Label: NAICSClassifier
Description: North American Industry Classification System code

Label: AddressLine
Description: A line of a street address
